tn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/f8eecd53264b0c8b68ef556c26ba8206.poster.avif?t=1732010153\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/f8eecd53264b0c8b68ef556c26ba8206.webm?t=1732010153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
